data.title: Hour 3 - Gus Johnson - The Dan Patrick Show
data.meta_description:
Dan Patrick discusses the issues of building an NFL roster after giving gigantic contracts to quarterbacks, as represented in Saquon Barkley leaving the Giants. FOX Sports Play-by-Play Voice Gus Johnson joins Dan to preview the college football season. Plus, Dan wraps up the conversation on phenoms.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
